org.springframework.data.gemfire.config.schema.support

Class ComposableSchemaObjectCollector

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.springframework.data.gemfire.config.schema.support.ComposableSchemaObjectCollector
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Iterable<SchemaObjectCollector<?>>, SchemaObjectCollector<java.lang.Object>

    public final class ComposableSchemaObjectCollector
extends java.lang.Object
implements SchemaObjectCollector<java.lang.Object>, java.lang.Iterable<SchemaObjectCollector<?>>
    The ComposableSchemaObjectCollector class is a SchemaObjectCollector implementation composed of multiple SchemaObjectCollector objects wrapped in a facade and treated like a single SchemaObjectCollector using the Composite Software Design Pattern.
    Since:
    2.0.0
    See Also:
    SchemaObjectCollector
